<p>Good evening and welcome to Sportsmail's live coverage of Wolves' trip to Bramall Lane for a clash with Sheffield United!</p>

<p>With both clubs getting their Premier League campaigns underway tonight, Nuno Espirito Santo and Chris Wilder will be keen to build on last season's top-half finishes by getting underway victory...</p>
